headline: J.B. Hunt and Eastern and Canadian railways see steady intermodal volume
summary: Intermodal volumes so far seem to be dodging the “air pocket” expected in the wake of steep tariffs on goods from China. The post J.B. Hunt and Eastern and Canadian railways see steady intermodal volume appeared first on FreightWaves.
